This paper discusses the practical challenges and current state of GANs, which are a popular topic in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions hyperparameter tuning and neural architecture engineering, which are common topics in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper also discusses reproducibility issues, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
